name: The Senley Chair
description: Conveying both a subtle opulence and a timeless elegance, the Senley brings gravitas and style to your dining room. The dark tinted beech of the frame and legs, sits satisfyingly alongside the more subtle tones of the upholstery. Tapered legs, a deep seat, and an angular backrest, framed by the bold finish, have created the Senley chair that exudes a self-assured sophistication. For a touch of high-end luxury, DAVIDSON offers the option upholstery in a fabric or leather of your choice, a perfect addition to your interior.
